data.description: WORKING HORSE/Animal RANCH.... 18+ Acres of Peaceful country ALL usable land.    Arena, work arena, riding pens, horse stalls, tack room, work sheds, chicken coops, dog runs/covered, hay barn, storage and more  You ONLY have to move in.. Well maintained grounds to make your transition so easy.  Low property taxes. Own your well. Cooperative lower priced electric. Septic system... If you have a ranch in the city... sell it!!! and move  to this quiet beautiful county Ranch.    You Will NOT !!! ever regret it.   Country style home with front and back covered porches. Beautiful mature trees giving it shade and blessings abound.    Room for your own country garden and with our mild seasons the amount of things that grow here is abundant.   This property is in the backyard of the Temecula Wine country but without the crazy traffic from all of the wineries.   This is must see for the serious animal lovers.  You would never get all of this for under 1.6M in other areas including wine country.  COME SEE!!!  You can see the owners/family love in this place (original owners)
